61 ma priego che m’addite la cagione, 62 sì ch’i’ la veggia e ch’i’ la mostri altrui; 63 ché nel cielo uno, e un qua giù la pone».

query.result:
**English:**
58 The world is indeed so deserted 59 of every virtue, as you seem to me, 60 and pregnant and covered with malice;
61 but I pray that you point out to me the cause, 62 so that I may see it and show it to others; 63 for one places it in heaven, and one down here».
**Sanskrit:**
