61 Api tu prārthayāmi yathā mama hetum ādiśeḥ, 62 Yathā aham tad paśyāmi anyeṣām ca darśayāmi; 63 Kimcid ekaḥ svarge sthāpayati, anyaḥ atraiva sthāpayati».

